    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing excellent lateral stability and steering feedback. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's known mechanical sensitivities. While it displays the minor cosmetic wear expected of a well-loved driver\u2019s car, its mechanical vitals and chassis rigidity remain excellent for spirited use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
