      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive shape. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor stone chips expected from responsible road use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cleanliness; the upholstery is supple with no tears, the dash is crack-free, and every button and dial functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it is robust, having followed a strict maintenance schedule\u2014the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts with precision, and the climate control is ice-cold. It has been a smoke-free, pet-free environment, ensuring a fresh feel for the next owner. This is a dependable, well-documented example that still has its best miles ahead of it.",
